{"tid":1386312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］最具威力的不合作運動上線！","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:42:02.000Z","uid":218734,"like":341,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"1f51fd363eaf2d17bdb982a43d874900afc8918b","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:11:23.000Z","msg":"（代友轉發，佢冇連登帳號)<br />\n<br />\n經過多個禮拜嘅奮鬥，大家都見到衝衝子甚至更多和理非已經唔L怕你血腥鎮壓，喺度僅此向咁多位默默付出嘅勇士致敬。但作為一個次次都有發夢嘅衝衝子，好希望大家一齊正視一個我發夢喺前線觀察到好現實嘅問題&mdash;<span style=\"color: red;\">就係經過連連征戰，同埋警狗大規模亂9拘捕後，不得不承認前線有變弱嘅跡象</span>，勇武傷嘅傷，日日都出黎打體力亦需要時間回復，而呢件係<span style=\"color: red;\">極需要正視嘅問題！</span><br />\n<br />\n看完國務院嘅記者會，國家高調撐警之後，<span style=\"color: red;\">警狗下一步必然更肆無忌憚鎮壓，有傳水炮車更在測試中！！手足長佔下風且危險重重！！我認為短期抗爭手法必須重新訂立</span>，轉轉策略讓和理非幫手buy time比衝衝子休養生息，置好裝，調整好策略再衝！！但有咩和理非方法有足夠嘅影響力呢？<br />\n<br />\n經過同航空界朋友相討後，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現上個星期嘅「和你飛」機場行動有好大嘅升級空間！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【不合作運動--直搗國際樞紐中心命脈：癱瘓機場！！】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n技術上做一個空城計既概念。班狗諗住喺街上面強力鎮壓示威者 <br />\n我地就打和理非牌<br />\n手無寸鐵！<span style=\"color: red;\">狗係機場清場成本極高</span>，你敢清，我豪比你！再打一場又有咩所謂！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「點樣將『和你飛』行動升級？」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地主打級超級和平牌，主要做法係逼爆曬合法既區域，包括旅客服務中心，食飯地方，離境大堂等，<span style=\"color: red;\">令到佢運作全部減速，令整個區域「非常擠塞」</span>，不論Check-in、寄存行李，甚至乎喺機場快線上落車既過程都變得「好慢好慢」，令所有人好耐都上唔到機，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">就一定會變成delay</span></span>。而當全部離境既客機都delay到仆街，外面就無機可入，佢地要排隊（放心問過現役香港機師，佢話唔會有危險因爲往香港客機可以飛往其他機場先。）<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋如果警方封住唯一出入機場既幾個入口</span>，又或者設路障逐架車去檢查，到時佢地一樣助攻到減慢成個香港機場已運作，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">等同幫手癱瘓機場。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n癱瘓香港國際機場有幾大影響，相信唔洗我多加分析。<br />\n但我一人之計，真係想不到更多更好嘅方法，希望各位同意嘅巴打比下意見。<br />\n<br />\n如果每個星期六都可以有一定人數入去搞到擠塞，相信威力一定更加大！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n想各位巴絲一齊討論下，睇下有冇咩建議？大家點睇！！"},{"pid":"e9e035db392de8a6a85bfd4a22d09403f2b32833","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:12:46.000Z","msg":"如果有兄弟姊妹有興趣一齊搞，可以交換下聯絡方式！"},{"pid":"623fc35843cb299f3b4b2b89fa88b83e2a79d2c0","tid":1386312,"uid":89898,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJA3BJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJA3BJH.jpg&h=bbbc6a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以全世界推post/連儂牆都見到呢張圖！<br />\n<br />\n尋日港澳辦開聲話係「保安問題」唔係「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">管治問題</span></span>」，我哋唔可以畀佢哋得逞，反而要煲大件事<br />\n<br />\n要提醒唔滿意黑社會嘅藍絲，呢單嘢係警黑合作<br />\n要提醒冇涉事嘅警犬，佢哋只係共產黨同鄉黑嘅走狗<br />\n要提醒有權但係唔投票嘅中立港豬，每一張vote out保皇派嘅票都好重要<br />\n要提醒淺黃嘅市民，解決到林鄭同有委員會係解決唔到問題<br />\n要提醒抗爭路上嘅手足，對準政權！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5eab575a68da74f978c132ef820e2a00b2436d","tid":1386312,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":56,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"On9? 機場可以直接當你恐襲用實彈"},{"pid":"df9da6761b20ecf3c6f02628fee112f5b165f226","tid":1386312,"uid":79793,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"0c5eab575a68da74f978c132ef820e2a00b2436d","tid":1386312,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":56,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:14:02.000Z","msg":"On9? 機場可以直接當你恐襲用實彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">P</span>"},{"pid":"441f7d14f930303d6b6c8342a67458e5c7a6ce19","tid":1386312,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不主動癱瘓"},{"pid":"eb93fb939cb1902e37faf1a5486a2ea8bf18ed70","tid":1386312,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"佢喺機場唔會拉你<br />\n但會閘青馬橋同機鐵站拉人"},{"pid":"90faa952f716d0bef99f8edea1082ad1769401b7","tid":1386312,"uid":115715,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"eb93fb939cb1902e37faf1a5486a2ea8bf18ed70","tid":1386312,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"佢喺機場唔會拉你<br />\n但會閘青馬橋同機鐵站拉人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"閘囉, 乜鳩裝備都冇"},{"pid":"71f8ebd2addd7f1b6e0efd9a08d88b82f4c2ed2d","tid":1386312,"uid":259945,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:19:14.000Z","msg":"想搵日入去機場71飲嘢<br />\n氣氛幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb3b6b9c00e9036a6ca83bf779d5869c67783eb","tid":1386312,"uid":219698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab6941c12c8a2c3c6b275a95f79cbef4fda56d1","tid":1386312,"uid":215419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:21:19.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"cc85447473af4419afe13d4cc8f195024bd51065","tid":1386312,"uid":76993,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"機場搞其實幾好<br />\n我就唔信班犬夠膽放TG同開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa2ce43b1709507f1f6788747a3a1bd0d0084ec","tid":1386312,"uid":239410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"一出水炮車，就癱瘓機場"},{"pid":"35e99559e7a31ec7f7e0603e2dab5d2ebafe5029","tid":1386312,"uid":281558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"可以順手阻埋入口生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c377b4ce469532ec4b8142a9ac5d5e9a6d56ac","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"幫手推下"},{"pid":"6b9660d690ecf6ca7767f32225796c5301f39634","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:33:30.000Z","msg":"大家有冇咩意見"},{"pid":"72d5cf8af916dcbcb76e27440b4f2a8b72830735","tid":1386312,"uid":277935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"多人就安全"},{"pid":"0db95b999b8cdb80d3af228efb4d9326024e796a","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e71341676b595c26b7f222121c3200f5fa3fc5ec","tid":1386312,"uid":284976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"借個靚位，入黎睇下有冇得搞thx<br />\n<br />\n[歡迎討論] 搵公司幫手推動罷工  入黎討論/屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386150</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a33e22087897ca37390072835e9cbf899d7268b2","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"434128f645c1dcecf5dcb8a6e6dd071b3b88444c","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd0aafc0862a40e22cea91c9edc43cbcc0b4e905","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"ff3262ff7d7f941848871812dc98423c1de2c457","tid":1386312,"uid":127328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:03:04.000Z","msg":"記住傳單要有英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874da731c40ddf6a573f3f467f083fa073deffc4","tid":1386312,"uid":218734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff3262ff7d7f941848871812dc98423c1de2c457","tid":1386312,"uid":127328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit